rows.label: tlk70000066_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Sheesh, how long's he gonna
keep me here waiting?

rows.label: tlk70000066_01_msg0002
rows.name:
He said he'd be right back, too!
How long does it take to salvage
a few bits and bobs in Gula?

rows.label: tlk70000066_01_msg0003
rows.name:
I've been standing around so long
I'm starting to get hungry...

rows.label: tlk70000066_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Hey, I think I saw some green
barrels around here earlier...

rows.label: tlk70000066_01_msg0006
rows.name:
You don't think they've got food in,
do you? Maybe I should go check... Not
like I've got much better to do...
